"A.P.238/4/9/12:30": "Stop there! That was great, that was really some good work."
"At first, I found your performance a little unsatisfactory..."
"But you were able to get over that and make it to the end, so you at least get to keep your job."
"Unfortunately, you're not good enough to get a raise, and I'm cutting down your vacation time."
"Now hurry up and head back, everyone is waiting for you!"
"That was an amazing! As much as I'd like to, I can't find any problems with your performance today."
"Your results definitely show your hard work and ambition in this organization!"
"Unfortunately for members of your caliber, I can't let you off the hook just yet."
"You think so too right? Claris Claes?"
"I definitely agree. I'll be granting your reward."
"Or that is to say, your reward is an exhibition match with me!"
"The fifth in the Council of Six and one of the Three Heroes, Claris Claes."
"I know it's great right? Be joyful, be honored."
"It's a rare chance to actually stand toe to toe with one of the Council of Six."
"Uh, Huey? They don't look that happy..."
"Don't worry, they're just nervous in your presence. They're completely in awe of you."
"If that's the case it can't be helped. Don't worry I'll take it reeeaaally easy on you."
"Alright, I'll face you with half, of half, of half of my power."
"Time to go! Claris Claes power mode half of a half of a half of a.... wait. How many was that?"
"Fine screw it. I'll just blow you to pieces!"
